title: Ronnie O'Sullivan 147 point break at Crucible Theatre
description:
Ronnie O&#039;Sullivan compiled a maximum 147 break at the World Championships here on Monday to seal his place in the quarter-finals.

The Englishman saved the best for last with his latest Crucible Theatre maximum coming in the final frame of his 13-7 win over Williams.

It was only the seventh maximum break recorded at the Crucible - the gifted O&#039;Sullivan has now struck three of them - and earned him a bonus of 147,000 (294,000 dollars) pounds plus 10,000 pounds (20,000 dollars) for the highest break of the tournament.
